A seventh-heaven experience for you and your loved one.

Do not miss an opportunity  to weave fond memories with your love at The Tamarind Tree. Book right away at +91 9888399994

From schoolmates to soulmates!

Madhu and Vishnu said YES to the endless possibilities of their stories, to the infectious joy they give each other.

Warms to our hearts to listen to such endearing stories, isn't it?

Weave your story into life at heritage wedding venue, The Tamarind Tree.

📷: @picturesbycinnamon 

For more, visit thetamarindtree.in or call us at +91 9888399994

#HumansofTTT #lovestorytheseries #valentinesmonth #weddingsaga #igtvvideos

Celebrate this Diwali with @anandsweetsindia❤️

Urvashi smiles at the comforting thought of going home - after a year of being away. She is excited to spend her Diwali with her family, reliving memories and experiences that make her soul smile. The past year has been challenging, being away from the people and places that bring us comfort. 

This Diwali, we hope you find joy as we take you down a memory lane of the good old times. To the days of waking up to the racket of rassi bombs, of helping Ma make laddus while sneaking an extra bite, of gathering together with your family in love and happiness, sharing memories and mithai. These are the simple pleasures that make Diwali extraordinary.

Discover the Diwali Ka Anand as we travel back in time to sweet, simple moments of eternity.

Videography: Karan Chawla @karannchawla 
Photography: Karan Anand @karananandd8
Creative Direction and Agency: Norm @norm_mag

latestPosts.caption:
The wedding at the Tamarind Tree was truly intimate and heartwarming, bringing together two large families and blending the rich traditions of Kannada and Marathi in a beautiful celebration. The decor by Tales of Traditions and the flawless makeup by Harshitha Reddy perfectly complemented the joyful atmosphere. Witnessing the couple and their families enjoy every moment was genuinely inspiring, and as photographers, we felt privileged to capture such a special and meaningful occasion.
.
